{"tid":651049,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[Poker] 有無巴打做賭場可以解答下","createTime":"2018-05-02T21:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T21:59:45.000Z","uid":181628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e42263581807903b560cdd0f08a2e2ac8cdf9944","tid":651049,"uid":181628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T21:59:45.000Z","msg":"玩咗Poker都一段時間<br />\n有玩過2card Holdem 同4 card Omaha<br />\n見到賭場有個叫 3 Card Poker 覺得幾好玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/055846_c279b8b27e223b8e3e6f40d2c1a62d6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F055846_c279b8b27e223b8e3e6f40d2c1a62d6a.jpg&h=14c44089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係因為如果Dealer 唔成牌 嬴既錢會少咗<br />\n所以想問下有無人計過 咩牌應該 call <br />\n咩牌應該唔放棄 <br />\n<br />\n我自己就咁諗<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">如果我一對都無 咁我比多200蚊去開牌<br />\n最多只可以嬴100蚊, <br />\n即係比100+200 嬴100 3賠1<br />\n但如果我有大牌先開牌<br />\n就好大機會嬴曬300蚊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不過有時大家都無牌 佢都係計我地嬴<br />\n所以我腦細就話其實應該係計200博200<br />\n所以比多200博100(嬴)+100(Anti)抵唔抵</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =腦細on99 夾硬計高自己個回報率 比自己賭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 腦細識玩 我on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}